STATE of North Carolina
v.
Coriante PIERCE No. 183P19-2 Supreme Court of North Carolina. August 22, 2019 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, For State of North Carolina. Coriante Pierce, For Pierce, Coriante. Roger A. Echols, District Attorney, For State of North Carolina.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 2nd of July 2019 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the North Carolina Court of Appeals, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the North Carolina Court of Appeals:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 14th of August 2019."
